Name: Delinea Secret Server
Author: Delinea
Description:
The [Delinea](https://delinea.com/) Secret Server Microsoft Sentinel Data Solution enables delivery of Delinea Secret Server log messages to your Microsoft Sentinel Workspace.

**Underlying Microsoft Technologies used:**

This solution takes a dependency on the following technologies, and some of these dependencies either may be in [Preview](https://azure.microsoft.com/support/legal/preview-supplemental-terms/) state or might result in additional ingestion or operational costs:

a. [Common Event Format (CEF) formatted logs in Microsoft Sentinel](https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/sentinel/connect-common-event-format)
